 children and three grandchildren all american speakers is a speakers bureau and booking agency providing information on booking marguerite kondracke for speaking engagements personal appearances and corporate events contact an all american speakers bureau booking agent for more information on marguerite kondracke speaking fees availability speech topics and cost to hire for your next event tag cloud booking agency famous corporate event appearance fees favorite celebrity speaker bureaus marguerite kondracke how to find hire schedule recommended entertainment contact special event keynote speakingmarguerite kondracke booking agency disclaimer marguerite kondracke booking agency celebrity appearance fees and availability contact a booking agent to check availability on marguerite kondracke and other top corporate entertainment exclusive buyers agent that books celebrities entertainers and speakers like marguerite kondracke for speaking engagements appearances and corporate events please note all american speakers bureau acts only as an entertainment brokerproducer for corporate functions private engagements and special events all american speakers bureau does not claim or represent itself as the exclusive agent or management of marguerite kondracke or any artist on this website speaker fees are determined based on a number of factors and may change without notice fees often vary based on a number of factors including speakers schedule supply and demand length of presentation location of event and other factors fee ranges listed on this website are intended to serve only as a guideline in some cases the actual price quote may be above or below the stated range all american speakers bureau is a celebrity booking agency and talent buyer which supplies celebrity talent worldwide we secure speakers and celebrities for speaking engagements advertising campaigns personal appearances commercials licensing voiceovers product endorsements spokesperson campaigns publicity event